OL,3,CBlood test could identify millions of
OL,4,Cpeople spreading tuberculosis
OL,5,Cunknowingly
OL,7,FShe said: "TB remains a global
OL,8,Fcatastrophe because our efforts to
OL,9,Fcontrol the spread are hindered by
OL,10,Finadequate testing, which is slow and
OL,11,Freliant on specialist equipment and
OL,12,Flabs.
OL,14,F"A third of people who get infected go
OL,15,Fundiagnosed and remain infectious.
OL,17,F"In our study, we combined a new
OL,18,Fmeasurement technique with deep
OL,19,Fmathematical analysis to identify
OL,20,Fthese six new markers of TB disease.
