OL,3,CBlood test could identify millions of
OL,4,Cpeople spreading tuberculosis
OL,5,Cunknowingly
OL,7,F"It could lead to a transformative
OL,8,Falternative to diagnosing the
OL,9,Fcondition ` a simple test that detects
OL,10,Fproteins in the bloodstream whose
OL,11,Flevels differ between people with TB,
OL,12,Fhealthy individuals and those
OL,13,Fsuffering from other respiratory
OL,14,Fillnesses."
OL,16,FShe explained that TB spreads through
OL,17,Finhaling tiny droplets from coughs or
OL,18,Fsneezes of infected people and while
OL,19,Fit mostly affects the lungs, it can
OL,20,Fdevastate any part of the body.
