OL,3,CBlood test could identify millions of
OL,4,Cpeople spreading tuberculosis
OL,5,Cunknowingly
OL,7,FCases in the UK increased to around
OL,8,F5,000 last year and are expected to
OL,9,Fcontinue rising in 2024, according to
OL,10,Fthe UK Health Security Agency.
OL,12,FThe study published in the Journal of
OL,13,FClinical Investigation Insight in time
OL,14,Ffor World TB day on March 24 involved
OL,15,Fan examination of proteins found in
OL,16,Fthe blood of people with active TB in
OL,17,FAfrica and South America.
