OL,3,CBlood test could identify millions of
OL,4,Cpeople spreading tuberculosis
OL,5,Cunknowingly
OL,7,FThe scientists compared the biomarkers
OL,8,Fto those found in healthy people and
OL,9,Fpatients with lung infections,
OL,10,Fidentifying 118 proteins that differed
OL,11,Fsignificantly between the groups.
OL,13,FThe experts then narrowed these down
OL,14,Fto the six proteins that, they say,
OL,15,Fcan be used to distinguish contagious
OL,16,Fpatients with TB from people in good
OL,17,Fhealth or with lung conditions.
